### PET IMAGE UPLOAD ENDPOINTS
### Requires authentication (JWT token)

@baseUrl = http://localhost:5000/api
@token = your_jwt_token_here
@petId = 1

### 1. Upload single image to a pet
POST {{baseUrl}}/pets/{{petId}}/images
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=----WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW

------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="files"; filename="dog.jpg"
Content-Type: image/jpeg

< ./path/to/your/image.jpg
------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW--

### 2. Upload multiple images to a pet (max 5 per pet)
POST {{baseUrl}}/pets/{{petId}}/images
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=----WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW

------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="files"; filename="dog1.jpg"
Content-Type: image/jpeg

< ./path/to/dog1.jpg
------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="files"; filename="dog2.jpg"
Content-Type: image/jpeg

< ./path/to/dog2.jpg
------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW--

### 3. Get all images for a pet
GET {{baseUrl}}/pets/{{petId}}/images

### 4. Delete an image from a pet
@imageId = 1
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/pets/{{petId}}/images/{{imageId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
